14/* RFC2672 */

16#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_DNAME_39_C
17#define RDATA_GENERIC_DNAME_39_C
18
19#define RRTYPE_DNAME_ATTRIBUTES (DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_SINGLETON)
20
21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_dname(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 dns_name_t name;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26
27 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
28
29 UNUSED(type);
30 UNUSED(rdclass);
31 UNUSED(callbacks);
32
33 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
34 false));
35
36 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
37 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
38 if (origin == NULL)
39 origin = dns_rootname;
40 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
41 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
42}
43
44static inline isc_result_t
45totext_dname(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
46 isc_region_t region;
47 dns_name_t name;
48 dns_name_t prefix;
49 bool sub;
50
51 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
52 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
53
54 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
55 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
56
57 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
58 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
59
60 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
61
62 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
63}
64
65static inline isc_result_t
66fromwire_dname(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
67 dns_name_t name;
68
69 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
70
71 UNUSED(type);
72 UNUSED(rdclass);
73
74 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
75
76 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
77 return(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
78}
79
80static inline isc_result_t
81towire_dname(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
82 dns_name_t name;
83 dns_offsets_t offsets;
84 isc_region_t region;
85
86 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
87 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
88
89 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
90 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
91 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
92 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
93
94 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
95}
96
97static inline int
98compare_dname(ARGS_COMPARE) {
99 dns_name_t name1;
100 dns_name_t name2;
101 isc_region_t region1;
102 isc_region_t region2;
103
104 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
105 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
106 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
107 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
108 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
109
110 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
111 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
112
113 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
114 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
115
116 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
117 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
118
119 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
120}
121
122static inline isc_result_t
123fromstruct_dname(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
124 dns_rdata_dname_t *dname = source;
125 isc_region_t region;
126
127 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
128 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
129 REQUIRE(dname->common.rdtype == type);
130 REQUIRE(dname->common.rdclass == rdclass);
131
132 UNUSED(type);
133 UNUSED(rdclass);
134
135 dns_name_toregion(&dname->dname, &region);
136 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
137}
138
139static inline isc_result_t
140tostruct_dname(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
141 isc_region_t region;
142 dns_rdata_dname_t *dname = target;
143 dns_name_t name;
144
145 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
146 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
147 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
148
149 dname->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
150 dname->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
151 ISC_LINK_INIT(&dname->common, link);
152
153 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
154 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
155 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
156 dns_name_init(&dname->dname, NULL);
157 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &dname->dname));
158 dname->mctx = mctx;
159 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
160}
161
162static inline void
163freestruct_dname(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
164 dns_rdata_dname_t *dname = source;
165
166 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
167 REQUIRE(dname->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_dname);
168
169 if (dname->mctx == NULL)
170 return;
171
172 dns_name_free(&dname->dname, dname->mctx);
173 dname->mctx = NULL;
174}
175
176static inline isc_result_t
177additionaldata_dname(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
178 UNUSED(rdata);
179 UNUSED(add);
180 UNUSED(arg);
181
182 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
183
184 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
185}
186
187static inline isc_result_t
188digest_dname(ARGS_DIGEST) {
189 isc_region_t r;
190 dns_name_t name;
191
192 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
193
194 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
195 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
196 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
197
198 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
199}
200
201static inline bool
202checkowner_dname(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
203
204 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
205
206 UNUSED(name);
207 UNUSED(type);
208 UNUSED(rdclass);
209 UNUSED(wildcard);
210
211 return (true);
212}
213
214static inline bool
215checknames_dname(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
216
217 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_dname);
218
219 UNUSED(rdata);
220 UNUSED(owner);
221 UNUSED(bad);
222
223 return (true);
224}
225
226static inline int
227casecompare_dname(ARGS_COMPARE) {
228 return (compare_dname(rdata1, rdata2));
229}
